# TypeScript test conventions

Follow `ai-kit/TEST_CONVENTIONS.md` (Vitest section).

- `describe` names the unit under test.
- `it('should ... when ...', ...)` for each case.
- Use `it.each` for table-driven cases.
- Add `// Given`, `// When`, `// Then` for non-trivial scenarios.
